results.name: Untouchable
results.title: Puma LaMelo Ball LaFrancé Amour Untouchable
results.description:
The Puma LaMelo Ball LaFrancé Amour Untouchable adds a Puma Black and Glowing Pink colorway to NBA star LaMelo Ball’s chunky, Y2K-inspired sneaker.

As part of a collaboration between Puma and Ball’s brand LaFrancé, the Untouchable Puma LaMelo Ball LaFrancé Amour sneaker embraces exaggerated silhouettes and oversized detailing. For instance, extra-wide black laces thread through the eyelets and create an overlapping pattern over the lace cage. Padding in the tongue and collar gives the sneaker a bulky appearance, while the thick EVA midsole furthers the exaggerated look and spans the full length of the shoe. Although the upper is crafted from a combination of leather, textile, and synthetic leather, the sockliner and insole are 100 percent textile.

Our experts like the bubble-like, graffiti-inspired LaFrancé branding on the midsole. The bulbous shapes match the oval textile detailing in Glowing Pink on the upper. The Puma LaMelo Ball LaFrancé Amour Untouchable was released on July 19, 2024, and retailed for $110.

results.name: Moment
results.title: Puma LaMelo Ball LaFrancé Amour Moment
results.description:
The Puma LaMelo Ball LaFrancé Amour Moment is an all-over-beige addition to NBA player LaMelo Ball’s signature LaFrancé lifestyle fashion label and Puma.

Incorporating elements from streetwear fashion and sportswear, this sneaker, the Moment Puma LaMelo Ball LaFrancé Amour, boasts an exaggerated silhouette with oversized cotton laces and chunky padding in the collar. The earth-toned Alpine Snow colorway complements the splashes of cream across the upper and lets the overlapping upper design take center stage. The internal EVA midsole stretches the entire length of the shoe, while the rubber cupsole adds stability. LaFrancé lettering in a light-brown hue can be found underfoot, on the tongue, and on the heel’s pull tab. Although the upper is crafted from leather and textile, the inner lining is made from a lightweight synthetic material.

Our experts like the textured outsole, which displays Puma and LaFrancé branding in gothic, graffiti-inspired lettering. The Puma LaMelo Ball LaFrancé Amour Moment was released on July 19, 2024, and sold for $110.

results.name: One Piece Straw Hat Luffy
results.title: Puma Suede One Piece Straw Hat Luffy
results.description:
The Puma Suede One Piece Straw Hat Luffy sneaker is a vibrant homage to the beloved protagonist of the iconic anime series, One Piece. Dressed in shades of feather grey and platinum grey, this sneaker captures the spirit of adventure and determination that Luffy embodies. Designed for fans who carry the essence of exploration and the dream of finding their own "One Piece," this edition marries the timeless appeal of Puma Suede with the adventurous heart of the Straw Hat crew.

Luffy, known for his unwavering resolve and charismatic leadership, inspires the design of this sneaker. The color palette, though understated, reflects the simplicity and depth of Luffy's character, offering a versatile look that can accompany fans on their own quests and daily adventures. The sneaker features subtle nods to the One Piece series that resonate with fans, making it a wearable piece of the saga they cherish.

Launched on March 23, 2024, for $85, the Puma Suede One Piece Straw Hat Luffy quickly sailed into the hearts of sneaker collectors and anime enthusiasts alike. Its release is celebrated as a moment when the paths of fashion and anime crossed, creating a sneaker that's not only a testament to Luffy's journey but also an invitation to wearers to set sail on their own adventures. This sneaker is a symbol of the journey, friendship, and dreams that define One Piece.

results.name: Red White
results.title: Puma Speedcat OG Red White
results.description:
The Puma Speedcat OG Red White is a bold performance shoe made for speed whose design was inspired by the racetrack.

The Red White Puma Speedcat OG has a lightweight paneled leather upper in Puma's bold For All Time Red color. A red leather overlay forms the toe cap, which also bears a white Puma logo on the outer side. White suede Puma Formstrip racing stripes appear on each side of the shoe above the red heel panel, while the Puma brand name and logo appear in metallic-gold letters on the outer side right above it. The tongue and heel also feature metallic-gold Puma branding. The rubber outsole is black and patterned for traction.

What we like best about this sneaker is the slim design that truly supports the speed-enhancing features. The Puma Speedcat OG Red White was first released on June 29, 2024, for an original price of $120.

results.name: Black White
results.title: Puma Speedcat OG Black White
results.description:
The Puma Speedcat OG Black White dresses this classic low-top sneaker from the early 2000s in a straightforward colorway of black and white.

Inspired by motorsports and Puma’s apparel partnerships with several F1 teams, this lifestyle shoe boasts a sleek, slim-fitting silhouette. The upper is crafted from premium suede in black with the signature formstrip in white reaching across the side panels. In addition, the Black White Puma Speedcat OG showcases subtle Puma branding, including ‘PUMA’ in metallic gold lettering on the lateral side panel and the tongue, and a white Jumping Cat logo on the toebox. The thin, rubber outsole comes in black and offers traction underfoot, while the black laces secure the closure.

Our experts like the sneaker’s overall premium feel created by the metallic gold accents set against the velvety suede upper. The Puma Speedcat OG Black White was released on June 29, 2024, and sold for $120.

results.name: Green Gecko
results.title: Puma LaMelo Ball MB.01 Lo Green Gecko
results.description:
The Puma LaMelo Ball MB01 Lo Green Gecko has become a part of the brand´s catalog. The basketball sneaker appears in a Green Gecko or Castlerock colorway.

The upper of this collaborative shoe is made from synthetic materials featuring a 3D printed design throughout. The laces are made of green cotton with an underlying tongue made of mesh. This upper displays a circular leaves motif, near the collar, forming a crown and the rubber outsole has a thin linear pattern for traction.

The Puma LaMelo Ball MB01 Lo Green Gecko was originally released on October 21, 2022. The retail price was $120.

results.name: One Piece Red-Haired Shanks
results.title: Puma Suede One Piece Red-Haired Shanks
results.description:
The Puma Suede One Piece Red-Haired Shanks is part of a collaboration between Puma and One Piece, a pirate-themed manga series created by Eiichiro Oda.​
​​
​The sneaker pays tribute to Red Haired Shanks, the chief of the Red Haired Pirates, through its colorway. Team Regal Red matches the character’s vibrant red hair, while Puma Silver can be found on the Red Haired Pirates’ flag. The suede upper features a debossed Puma Cat logo on one side panel and a metallic silver skull and swords on the heel. The side panels feature a wavy leather line in silver with a teal outline. The tongue displays co-branding, including a skull and Puma lettering. In addition, three black lines that resemble claw marks can be found on the lateral side panel.​
​​
​Our StockX experts like the flat lace closure and the inclusion of Team Regal red laces. The Puma Suede One Piece Red-Haired Shanks was released on March 23rd, 2024, and retailed at $85.

results.name: Black White
results.title: Puma Suede Classic XXI Black White
results.description:
Like its predecessors, the Puma Suede Classic XXI Black White boasts a construction made of soft suede. However, this suede is sourced from an environmentally sustainable leather manufacturer.

The Black White Puma Suede Classic XXI pays homage to the original Suede released in 1968 through its upper design. The sneaker’s Puma Black and Puma White colorway gives the shoe a retro feel, while the rubber outsole provides extra traction and grip. In terms of branding, ‘PUMA SUEDE’ in gold lettering runs along the side overlays and matches the Puma logo on the heel tab. The suede tongue peeks out from behind the laces and displays a logo tag with ‘PUMA’ and the Puma logo.

Our experts like the full lace closure with black laces that secures the low-top shoe without adding bulk to the sleek silhouette. The Puma Suede Classic XXI Black White was released on February 19th, 2021, and retailed at $70.

results.name: One Piece Buggy
results.title: Puma Suede One Piece Buggy
results.description:
The Puma Suede One Piece Buggy is a low-top sneaker that’s part of a collaboration between Puma and One Piece, an anime and manga series that centers on the adventures of a young pirate and his crew.

This sneaker features a hairy suede upper in For All Time Red with perforations on the side panels and a long lace cage. Thick laces in For All Time Red wind through the eyelets and create a secure, adjustable closure. The sides display a shaggy suede panel in Ultra Blue that looks like a wave. Hits of metallic gold can be found on the skull logo on the heel and the "PUMA SUEDE" lettering on the side panel.

Our StockX experts like that the shaggy suede tongue is debossed with Puma branding but doesn’t feature metallic gold. The Puma Suede One Piece Buggy was released on March 23, 2024, and sold for $85.

results.name: Galaxy
results.title: Puma LaMelo Ball MB.01 Galaxy
results.description:
The Puma LaMelo Ball MB.01 Galaxy arrives with a galaxy-patterned mesh upper with reinforced purple overlays and sharp orange detailing. On the tongue, LaMelo's signature "One of One" graphic boasts neon colors, contrasting its dark, spacey background. At the base, a neon green sole offers enhanced court grip and durability.

The Puma LaMelo Ball MB.01 Galaxy released in April of 2022 and retailed for $125.

results.name: One Piece Blackbeard Teech
results.title: Puma Suede One Piece Blackbeard Teech
results.description:
The Puma Suede One Piece Blackbeard Teech sneaker is a daring fusion of Puma's classic style with the dark allure of one of the most formidable characters from the beloved anime series, One Piece. Decked in puma black and dark chocolate, this edition captures the essence of Marshall D. Teach, aka Blackbeard, with its bold and brooding color scheme. Designed for fans who appreciate the depth of storytelling and the complexity of character development in One Piece, this sneaker is a tribute to the series' iconic antagonist.

Crafted with the legendary Puma Suede silhouette, this sneaker offers timeless style coupled with modern design elements inspired by the One Piece universe. The choice of colors represents Blackbeard's menacing presence and his pivotal role in the series, providing fans with a piece of wearable art that's both stylish and symbolic. It's a perfect blend of streetwear fashion and anime culture, appealing to those who live at the intersection of comfort, style, and fandom.

Released on March 23, 2024, for $85, the Puma Suede One Piece Blackbeard Teech quickly became a coveted item among both sneaker enthusiasts and anime fans. Its launch is celebrated as a moment when Puma seamlessly integrated the spirit of One Piece into their classic suede design, offering a sneaker that's statement of allegiance to one of anime's most compelling narratives. This sneaker is a declaration of style and a nod to the enduring legacy of One Piece.

results.name: For All Time Red
results.title: Puma LaMelo Ball LaFrancé Amour Red
results.description:
The Puma LaMelo Ball LaFrancé Amour For All Time Red is part of the Puma x LaFrancé collaboration, which expresses NBA player LaMelo Ball’s personal style through the exaggerated silhouettes LaFrancé is known for.

Like other footwear in the collection, the For All Time Red Puma LaMelo Ball LaFrancé Amour features an all-over red colorway of For All Time Red. Reminiscent of Y2K fashion, thick padding in the collar and side panels gives the sneaker a chunky aesthetic. The upper boasts a durable canvas base with overlays in shiny patent leather. The full-length internal EVA midsole adds cushioning, while the fully wrapped rubber cupsole provides stability. The midsole and outsole display branding specific to LaMelo Ball and ‘LaFrancé’ provides the traction pattern underfoot.

Our StockX experts like the oversized, red laces, which match LaFrancé’s preference for exaggerated proportions. The Puma LaMelo Ball LaFrancé Amour For All Time Red was released on May 17, 2024, and sold for $120.

results.name: Not From Here Red Blast
results.title: Puma LaMelo Ball MB.01 Not From Here Red Blast
results.description:
Presented in a vibrant Red Blast color scheme, the Puma MB.01 takes cues from LaMelo Ball's "1 of 1" chest tattoo. Embroidery on the mesh upper represents the bird wings found in the tattoo, while the illustration on the tongue depicts a toned-down rendition of the exact design.

The Puma MB.01 Red Blast released in December of 2021 and retailed for $125.

results.name: Rick & Morty Adventures
results.title: Puma LaMelo Ball MB.02 Rick & Morty Adventures
results.description:
Rick and Morty are back for 2023 NBA All-Star Weekend, collaborating with Puma and LaMelo Ball for the release of the Puma LaMelo Ball MB.02 Rick & Morty Adventures sneaker.

LaMelo Ball's signature sneaker is getting a mismatch treatment with the right sneaker coming in a red to yellow gradient colorway, and the left featuring a gradient purple to green. Rick Sanchez sits on top of the tongue of the left sneaker while Morty Smith is placed on the right.

The Puma LaMelo Ball MB.02 Rick & Morty Adventures released February 17, 2023, with a retail price of $130.

results.name: Toxic
results.title: Puma LaMelo Ball MB.03 Toxic
results.description:
The Puma LaMelo Ball MB.03 Toxic effortlessly combines style and functionality, taking inspiration from an extraterrestrial realm. The design integrates bold elements such as slime and claw marks, creating a visually aggressive aesthetic.

With slime-inspired rubber wrap-ups and an engineered knit upper featuring scratch cutout, the Puma LaMelo Ball MB.03 Toxic showcases a vibrant Purple Glimmer-Green Gecko color combination. The spotlight is on NITROFOAM, a nitrogen-infused foam providing responsive cushioning in a lightweight configuration. The durability and comfort of the shoe are enhanced by the engineered mesh upper and TPU heel counter. A high abrasion, non-slip rubber outsole guarantees excellent traction, and personalized LaMelo Ball branding adds a distinctive touch.

The standout feature of the Puma LaMelo Ball MB.03 Toxic is the NITROFOAM Infused midsole, introducing innovative technology that delivers superior responsiveness and comfort while maintaining a lightweight profile. The sneaker was originally sold for $125 on October 27th, 2023.

results.name: Golden Child
results.title: Puma LaMelo Ball MB.01 Golden Child
results.description:
The Puma LaMelo Ball MB.01Golden Child is a limited-edition sneaker inspired by NBA star LaMelo Ball’s first sneaker with Puma. From the basketball player’s Rare Reserve Collection, this sneaker was once player-exclusive (PE).

The Golden Child iteration of the LaMelo Ball x Puma MB.01 features an upper of dusty gold monomesh with welded metallic gold overlays that lend both support and structure. An embroidered rocket ship flame design adorns the collar, a nod to Melo’s spaceship tattoo. Metallic TPU in gold covers the midsole composed of Puma NITROFOAM, designed for ultimate responsiveness and superior lightweight comfort. The outsole is made of a non-slip rubber compound patterned for impact absorption, enhanced durability, and multidirectional traction.

What we enjoy most about these Puma sneakers are the hits of LaMelo branding. His signature wings grace the tongue and his motto "1 of 1" is printed on the medial side toe cap. The word RARE appears in orange beneath the translucent rubber of the outsole. The Puma LaMelo Ball MB.01Golden Child was released on November 24, 2023, for a retail price of $140.

results.name: Dexter's Laboratory
results.title: Puma LaMelo Ball MB.03 Dexter's Laboratory
results.description:
Embark on a journey of style and performance with the Puma LaMelo Ball MB.03 Dexter's Laboratory edition. Inspired by the animated charm of Dexter's Laboratory, this sneaker is a vibrant mix of Poison Pink and Fluro Orange Pes, creating a visually striking appearance. Designed for dynamic play, the MB.03 Dexter's Laboratory edition offers superior cushioning, agile support, and a playful yet bold aesthetic that stands out both on and off the court.

Reflecting the energy and uniqueness of LaMelo Ball's personality, this sneaker is more than just footwear; it's a statement. Its sleek design, combined with the advanced performance features of Puma, ensures comfort and style. The sneaker's color palette and theme are a tribute to those who embrace their individuality and dare to be different in their fashion choices.

Launched on December 22, 2023, with a retail price of $135, the Puma LaMelo Ball MB.03 Dexter's Laboratory is a must-have for sneaker enthusiasts. It's a perfect blend of modern basketball technology and a touch of nostalgic animation, bringing a unique twist to the sneaker game.
